node.text:
A lil photo dump for y’all to enjoy !👾 Also Happy July ! It’s a baddies birth month…. 
These wings were unknowingly taken from @fancyfairyangela photo & edited by a third party, and in exchange for letting this image stay up she would like to ask everyone to please respect artists' images and not take photos like this from Pinterest or Google Images as everything there belongs to someone.
The PicsArt Stickers are also loaded with infringing content because they don't do enough to prevent or enforce copyright, everything is uploaded by users who might not know any better and these wings frequently show up there.
Please get permission from the owner before editing and publicly posting content found online, or get fairy wing overlays directly from her store.
Art theft is a growing problem for her and many small artists especially after last year, please don't make their struggle more difficult

node.text:
This is for all the Baklas 🌈✨🤍 because we all deserve our own @nylonmanila Covers ☀️🇵🇭 I worked on this with an entire team of Filipino creatives, from the Filipino banters behind the scene, the bibinka and jollibee we had for lunch and being on FaceTime with Manila the whole day- this project was as Filipino through and through 🇵🇭 2/5 covers hehehe
All the credits goes to them 
Creative direction and cover story: @angelordecartagena 

Photography: @raenbadua 

Fashion and Beauty Direction: @lynalumno 

Styling: @nikkopanti & @angelordecartagena 

Assisted by: Adrianne Chan

Makeup: @houseofdaphne 

Hair: @jojodidit 

Videography: @francisgum
